## Usage

```ts
import { identityService, identityGuard } from './src/identity/index.js';

// OIDC callback example
const result = await identityService.login('google', {
  code: 'auth-code',
  redirectUri: process.env.GOOGLE_REDIRECT_URI,
});

// Protect routes
app.addHook('preHandler', identityGuard);
```

## Environment

Configure provider credentials in `.env.example`.

## Base auth

Use `my add auth` for JWT, refresh tokens, MFA, and local credentials.
Use `my add enterprise-auth` for SSO and enterprise IdP integration.
